1952;;The Black Castle;;American;;Nathan H. Juran;;Richard Greene, Boris Karloff, Stephen McNally;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Black_Castle;;Sir Ronald Burton (Greene), a British gentleman, investigates the disappearance of two of his friends at the Austrian estate of the sinister Count von Bruno (McNally). Bruno secretly seeks revenge against the leaders of a British force that set the natives against him in colonial Africa: Burton's missing friends are among Bruno's victims, and Burton is now also in the trap. Burton plans to escape with Bruno's abused Countess, but the Count's henchmen bar the way.